  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    PythonCommandType
    Option list for choosing the method to connecting to Python.

    PYTHON, PYTHON2, and PYTHON3 all represent the command used to call Python from a termianl (using the commands python, python2, and python3, respectively).

    PYTHON_OTHER is used to indicate an 'other' command alias.

    PYTHON_PATH is used to indicate that an absolute path will be given to the desired Python executable.
